988426559,"angle":0,"y":24506.836476990644,"width":90.931275641434141},{"seed":2028389461,"strokeStyle":"solid","id":"xKmqvjyZnQQWFcf5Whb2e","strokeWidth":2,"roughness":0,"isDeleted":false,"fontSize":20,"opacity":100,"verticalAlign":"top","updated":1775623780965,"locked":false,"text":"We can build a trie out of abuses\nand in just O(n) traversal mask the abuses.\n\nFor each character in text we iterate through trie\nevery time we get ' _ , , , ' etc we reset our\ntrie iteration (to the top)\n\nif the abuse is found and next\nchar is EOS or non-alphabet, we reset our\ntrie iteration (to the top)\n\nif the abuse is found and next\nchar is EOS or non-alphabet, we\nmask and write to the new string. Else the word copied as is.\n\nThe final string is then sent\/broadcasted to the every participant.\n\nIt's O(N).\n ","version":167,"autoResize":true,"type":"text","backgroundColor":"transparent","index":"bEM","roundness":null,"containerId":null,"originalText":"We can build a trie out of abuses\nand in just O(n) traversal mask the abuses.\n\nFor each character in text we iterate through trie\nevery time we get ' _ , , , ' etc we reset our\ntrie iteration (to the top)\n\nif the abuse is found and next\nchar is EOS or non-alphabet, we reset our\ntrie iteration (to the top)\n\nif the abuse is found and next\nchar is EOS or non-alphabet, we\nmask and write to the new string. Else the word copied as is.\n\nThe final string is then sent\/broadcasted to the every participant.\n\nIt's O(N).\n ","height":475,"link":null,"strokeColor":"#1e1e1e","fillStyle":"solid","groupIds":[],"versionNonce":1881627637,"textAlign":"left","fontFamily":8,"lineHeight":1.25,"frameId":null,"boundElements":[],"x":1588.2538947109124,"angle":0,"y":24238.639660289453,"width":737},{"seed":530320245,"strokeStyle":"solid","id":"GWxWlzMv43mUhibzzhlNx","strokeWidth":2,"roughness":0,"isDeleted":false,"fontSize":20,"opacity":100,"verticalAlign":"top","updated":1775623621898,"locked":false,"text":"mondays are shit","v